message.text:
𝐉𝐨𝐢𝐧 𝐔𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐧𝐧𝐨𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧! 

Are you ready to 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑 into the dynamic world of hospitality and tourism? 

We invite you to be part of an exciting event on:
🗓️𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟒, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 (Wednesday)
⏰ 1:00 PM-5:00 PM
📍 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦, 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚

This year’s theme, 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”, is your chance to explore how innovation can shape our vibrant industries, brought to you by 𝐊𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬! 

Whether you’re an aspiring Entrepreneur, HRM and Tourism Students, this event is designed to inspire and equip you with the tools you need to thrive!

So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit! 

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐱𝐜𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!

E-certificates will be provided to all attendees.

𝐉𝐨𝐢𝐧 𝐔𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐧𝐧𝐨𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧! 

Are you ready to 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑 into the dynamic world of hospitality and tourism? 

We invite you to be part of an exciting event on:
🗓️𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟒, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 (Wednesday)
⏰ 1:00 PM-5:00 PM
📍 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦, 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚

This year’s theme, 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”, is your chance to explore how innovation can shape our vibrant industries, brought to you by 𝐊𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬! 

Whether you’re an aspiring Entrepreneur, HRM and Tourism Students, this event is designed to inspire and equip you with the tools you need to thrive!

So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit! 

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐱𝐜𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!

E-certificates will be provided to all attendees.

https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=3F6kgO7V4EaddTfEe-m3zM3QzDs0peRLmijvCfcM1HlUNjRVQk9STTdVUU1LWTNWMUJQMlZWOEhVRS4u

message.text:
🫣 Open-minded ka ba? 🫣

Good day! We are 4th-year marketing students from FEU Diliman, and we are conducting our Thesis survey on The Role of Integrated Marketing Communication Tools in Promoting Male Contraceptive to Filipino Customers 👌🏻.

We would be grateful if you could accomplish our survey and share your insights.

Qualifications:

🎈 You are aged 21 to 28 years old.
🎈 You currently reside in Metro Manila.
🎈 You have seen at least one condom-related advertisement on social media that uses humor.

❗️If you are qualified, you may access this Google Form link:
https://forms.gle/eBKqCJZmG8A7TW5U7

Your participation is greatly appreciated. All information will be kept confidential and shall only be used for educational purposes. Thank you so much for your help!

message.text:
🫣 Open-minded ka ba? 🫣

Good day! We are 4th-year marketing students from FEU Diliman, and we are conducting our Thesis survey on The Role of Integrated Marketing Communication Tools in Promoting Male Contraceptive to Filipino Customers 👌🏻.

We would be grateful if you could accomplish our survey and share your insights.

Qualifications:

🎈 You are aged 21 to 28 years old.
🎈 You currently reside in Metro Manila.
🎈 You have seen at least one condom-related advertisement on social media that uses humor.

❗️If you are qualified, you may access this Google Form link:
https://forms.gle/eBKqCJZmG8A7TW5U7

Your participation is greatly appreciated. All information will be kept confidential and shall only be used for educational purposes. Thank you so much for your help!

message.text:
TAMARAWS, LUSOB SA LUNETA!
BURUKRATA-KAPITALISMO, IBAGSAK!

Sa bawat pagbaha, lantad ang kabulukan ng estado: walang trabaho, walang tirahan, walang buhay na ligtas. Samantalang ang mga burukrata-kapitalista—sagad sa negosyo, sagad sa tubo!

Hindi baha ang tunay na kalaban, kundi ang bulok na sistemang pinapalakas ng US-Marcos-Duterte! Kaya’t lusob, bahain natin ng protesta ang lansangan!

Setyembre 21, 2025 | Luneta, 9AM
#KurakotManagot
#Lusob

Sign up form: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfWeYfs_2IOTiP_TMbhueHPyoK36HJq9QhE3sUA-yo5roD7uQ/viewform 

O I-scan ang QR para makasali!
